WEBVTT

00:01.248 --> 00:02.750
[MOUSE SQUEAKS]

00:02.817 --> 00:04.819
[PENGUINS CHIRP]

00:06.387 --> 00:08.389
[ALL CHEERING]

00:10.558 --> 00:11.559
[SCREECHES]

00:13.627 --> 00:14.697
♪ Adventure Time ♪

00:14.762 --> 00:16.332
♪ Come on, grab your friends ♪

00:16.397 --> 00:18.843
♪ We'll go to very distant lands ♪

00:18.899 --> 00:21.175
♪ With Jake the dog
and Finn the human ♪

00:21.235 --> 00:23.010
♪ The fun will never end ♪

00:23.070 --> 00:25.175
♪ It's Adventure Time ♪

00:33.113 --> 00:34.558
[WATER DRIPPING, ECHOING]

00:34.615 --> 00:36.288
Do you think it's right for Marceline

00:36.350 --> 00:38.387
to invite us to jam
without Princess and Beemo?

00:38.452 --> 00:40.056
It's just a jam sesh.

00:40.120 --> 00:41.724
Is that what you're gonna
jam with?

00:41.789 --> 00:44.167
Yeah, man.
Balloon music is the future.

00:44.225 --> 00:45.260
Listen.

00:45.326 --> 00:48.102
[BALLOON SQUEAKING]

00:48.162 --> 00:50.335
[RAPPING]
♪ Shake your extremities ♪

00:50.397 --> 00:52.172
♪ Shake your extremities ♪

00:52.233 --> 00:53.712
♪ All your arms and knees ♪

00:53.767 --> 00:55.872
♪ I want 'em shakin',
baby, please ♪

00:55.936 --> 00:58.109
♪ Baby, shake your eyes for me ♪

00:58.172 --> 01:00.243
♪ Shake your eyes for me ♪

01:00.307 --> 01:01.752
♪ Shake your eyes
for me ♪

01:01.809 --> 01:03.880
♪ Shake your eyes for free ♪

01:03.944 --> 01:06.049
♪ Now make some bills,
make duck bills ♪

01:06.113 --> 01:07.649
♪ Make 'em ill,
quack me up ♪

01:07.715 --> 01:08.853
- [QUACKS]
- ♪ With some yolks ♪

01:08.916 --> 01:10.918
♪ I like girls
who know the ropes ♪

01:10.985 --> 01:12.896
♪ I like girls who can cope ♪

01:12.953 --> 01:15.695
♪ with the futuristic sound ♪

01:15.756 --> 01:19.863
♪ of balloon music ♪

01:19.927 --> 01:21.998
Pretty good.

01:22.062 --> 01:24.008
I don't think
you've mastered it yet.

01:24.064 --> 01:26.010
Well, duh.
I just started.

01:26.066 --> 01:27.943
Oh, dude.
Here's a note.

01:28.002 --> 01:29.447
What's it say?

01:29.503 --> 01:32.074
"Hey, guys, I had to run out,
but I'll be back.

01:32.139 --> 01:33.447
Blee bloo blop.

01:33.507 --> 01:35.111
Don't go in my house."

01:35.175 --> 01:36.711
- That's it?
- Yeah.

01:36.777 --> 01:38.814
Just "don't go in my house"
in all caps --

01:38.879 --> 01:40.517
written in blood.

01:40.581 --> 01:41.685
Hmm.

01:41.749 --> 01:43.751
[BALLOON SQUEAKING]

01:47.388 --> 01:48.628
What are you doing?

01:48.689 --> 01:50.828
Eliminating desire from my heart.

01:50.891 --> 01:52.495
It helps pass the time.

01:52.559 --> 01:53.833
Come on.
I can't do that.

01:53.894 --> 01:55.532
Let's play cloud hunt
'til she gets here.

01:55.596 --> 01:57.872
No, man, I got a mental block
with cloud hunt.

01:57.932 --> 01:59.570
Yeah, that's what makes it awesome --

01:59.633 --> 02:01.169
'cause I know I'll win.

02:01.235 --> 02:03.442
Oh, what?!
Bring it on, brother!

02:03.504 --> 02:05.609
Now, explain the rules,
'cause I forget.

02:05.673 --> 02:08.119
Okay. I count to 10
and you go hide somewhere.

02:08.175 --> 02:10.211
Then I got to try to find you.

02:10.276 --> 02:11.722
You can hide...

02:11.779 --> 02:14.453
you can hide anywhere in here.

02:14.515 --> 02:16.017
Anywhere in here.

02:16.083 --> 02:17.926
But Marcy's house is off-limits,

02:17.985 --> 02:20.329
because she said so, okay?
- Got it.

02:20.387 --> 02:22.367
Okay, I'm gonna start
counting.

02:22.423 --> 02:24.027
Ready?

02:24.091 --> 02:24.933
Yes.

02:24.992 --> 02:25.834
Go!

02:25.893 --> 02:27.099
One...

02:27.161 --> 02:28.697
two...

02:28.762 --> 02:30.264
three...

02:30.331 --> 02:31.742
four...

02:31.799 --> 02:32.800
five...

02:32.866 --> 02:33.867
four...

02:33.934 --> 02:35.675
Over the mountain
the ominous cloud,

02:35.736 --> 02:37.977
coming to cover the land
in a shroud.

02:38.038 --> 02:39.847
Hide in a bushel,
a basement, a cave,

02:39.907 --> 02:41.750
but when cloud comes a-huntin',

02:41.809 --> 02:43.755
no one's a-save!

02:43.811 --> 02:45.290
No -- safe.

02:45.346 --> 02:46.757
Cloud hunt...

02:46.814 --> 02:48.088
gotcha!

02:48.148 --> 02:49.491
Huh.

02:49.550 --> 02:50.824
Hmm.

02:50.884 --> 02:51.885
Aha!

02:53.153 --> 02:55.155
[WATER SPLASHING]

02:57.725 --> 02:59.398
Jake! Get out of there!

02:59.460 --> 03:01.064
Marceline's gonna kill you!

03:01.128 --> 03:03.404
Jake!
I know this isn't a mirror!

03:03.464 --> 03:04.841
What the --

03:04.898 --> 03:06.605
You're doing it wrong, even!

03:06.667 --> 03:10.046
Get out! Get out!

03:10.104 --> 03:11.742
[CAT DOOR OPENS]

03:11.805 --> 03:13.284
Dude, get out of there!
She's gonna kill us!

03:13.340 --> 03:15.115
She could be home any minute!
Did you read the note?!

03:15.175 --> 03:16.654
I mean, you read the note!
You told it to me!

03:16.710 --> 03:17.654
[RUSTLING]

03:17.711 --> 03:18.712
[GASPS]

03:20.280 --> 03:23.022
[SWITCH CLICKS]

03:23.083 --> 03:24.027
[SNIFFS]

03:24.084 --> 03:27.088
Smells like sourdough in here.

03:27.154 --> 03:28.360
She's gonna kill us!

03:28.422 --> 03:30.026
Once she finds out,
she's gonna tie us up

03:30.090 --> 03:31.364
and eat us like a spider!

03:31.425 --> 03:33.735
You don't think I know that?

03:33.794 --> 03:34.795
Hurmmmmm.

03:36.263 --> 03:38.072
We'll wait for the right moment
and sneak out,

03:38.132 --> 03:40.237
right under her big, fat caboose.

03:40.300 --> 03:42.906
Okay, man.
I can do this.

03:42.970 --> 03:43.971
[GRUNTING]

03:45.839 --> 03:47.785
Shh! Here she comes!

03:50.044 --> 03:52.957
- Here she comes!
- Shh! Shhh!

03:53.013 --> 03:54.014
[SNIFFS]

03:55.149 --> 03:57.129
[SWITCH CLICKS]

03:57.184 --> 03:58.185
[SNIFFS]

03:59.586 --> 04:00.587
Huh.

04:02.489 --> 04:03.832
[DOOR CLOSES, TOILET LID CLUNKS]

04:03.891 --> 04:04.801
[ZIPPER OPENS]

04:04.858 --> 04:06.098
[LIQUID SPLASHING]

04:06.160 --> 04:07.264
Let's get outta here!

04:07.327 --> 04:08.863
[DOOR CREAKS]

04:08.929 --> 04:11.205
[SPLASHING STOPS, RESUMES]

04:11.265 --> 04:12.266
[DOOR CREAKS]

04:12.332 --> 04:14.175
[SPLASHING STOPS]
MARCELINE: Hello?

04:14.234 --> 04:16.077
[TOILET FLUSHES]

04:16.136 --> 04:17.615
She didn't wash hands!

04:17.671 --> 04:20.515
Is someone here?

04:20.574 --> 04:22.178
[SNIFFS]

04:22.242 --> 04:24.244
[SNIFFING]

04:29.583 --> 04:32.826
That's what stinks!

04:32.886 --> 04:34.923
Where are those dweebs?

04:34.988 --> 04:36.228
[CELLPHONE BEEPS]

04:36.290 --> 04:37.291
[RINGING]

04:38.692 --> 04:40.694
[TELEPHONE RINGING]

04:42.463 --> 04:44.568
[ANSWERING MACHINE CLICKS]

04:44.631 --> 04:46.736
- FINN: This is Jake!
- JAKE: And this is Finn!

04:46.800 --> 04:48.780
[BOTH LAUGH]

04:48.836 --> 04:50.975
BOTH: We're not home
right now, so...

04:51.038 --> 04:53.018
[BOTH LAUGH]

04:53.073 --> 04:54.950
[BOTH LAUGH]

04:55.008 --> 04:56.009
<i>...leave a message!</i>

04:56.076 --> 04:57.953
[MUFFLED LAUGHTER]

04:58.011 --> 04:59.115
Shh.

04:59.179 --> 05:01.181
BOTH: <i>...leave a message!</i>
[BEEP]

05:01.248 --> 05:03.319
Uh... y-yeah.

05:03.383 --> 05:05.363
Hey, you guys.
Are you still coming over?

05:05.419 --> 05:08.889
It's jam time, so, like,
call me, 'Kay??

05:08.956 --> 05:10.697
[CELLPHONE BEEPS]

05:10.757 --> 05:12.759
[SHORTS]

05:15.362 --> 05:16.397
[SNAPS FINGERS]

05:16.463 --> 05:18.465
[SPLAT]

05:20.434 --> 05:21.435
[RUSTLING]

05:23.770 --> 05:25.477
[RUSTLING, PAPER CRINKLES]

05:25.539 --> 05:26.984
Whatcha doin'?

05:27.040 --> 05:29.042
Turn around.

05:32.446 --> 05:35.222
When she gets this, she'll leave
and we can escape.

05:35.282 --> 05:37.319
Brilliant!
But how's it gonna work?

05:37.384 --> 05:39.386
I'll fly the paper
as an airplane

05:39.453 --> 05:41.160
down the bedroom ladder.

05:41.221 --> 05:43.030
It'll triple-barrel-roll past
the kitchen,

05:43.090 --> 05:44.933
open the fridge
and cook some eggs,

05:44.992 --> 05:46.835
then eat the eggs and unfold itself

05:46.894 --> 05:49.704
as it lays on the carpet in
front of Marceline's door.

05:49.763 --> 05:52.073
Yeah, yeah!
Awesome! Yeah!

