06:14.788 --> 06:16.893
No! Nu-- nuts!

06:16.957 --> 06:18.334
[SIGHS]

06:18.392 --> 06:20.565
Well, if they're not
gonna show up,

06:20.627 --> 06:23.608
then I'll just work
on my own stuff, I guess.

06:23.664 --> 06:25.803
[BASS PLAYS]

06:25.866 --> 06:27.004
[CLEARS THROAT]

06:27.067 --> 06:28.876
Take one for new concept album

06:28.936 --> 06:31.143
based on 500 years
of my journal entries.

06:31.205 --> 06:33.151
So here's some preliminary notes.

06:33.207 --> 06:34.811
I...

06:34.875 --> 06:37.481
I want to make this the most
emotional album ever --

06:37.544 --> 06:40.650
so private and secret that
I'll never let anyone hear.

06:40.714 --> 06:42.421
This is so wrong.

06:42.482 --> 06:45.691
No one can ever hear it!
Ever!

06:45.752 --> 06:46.958
[DRUMBEAT PLAYS]

06:47.020 --> 06:49.022
Take one.

06:51.124 --> 06:52.933
♪ Hello, journal, it's me ♪

06:52.993 --> 06:54.995
♪ It's been a while since we talked

06:55.062 --> 07:00.011
about my life and stuff ♪

07:01.635 --> 07:04.582
♪ Let's start with my feelings
about my friends ♪

07:04.638 --> 07:06.049
I' Oh, Wait I'

07:06.106 --> 07:10.145
♪ I don't have friends ♪

07:10.210 --> 07:12.156
We've crossed the line!

07:12.212 --> 07:13.816
I'm getting out of here, man!

07:13.880 --> 07:15.257
Yeah! Do it!

07:15.315 --> 07:17.386
MARCELINE:
♪ Because they don't know what it's like ♪

07:17.451 --> 07:21.456
♪ to live forever ♪

07:23.790 --> 07:26.600
♪ and forget who you even are

07:26.660 --> 07:28.606
and what you think about
anything ♪

07:28.662 --> 07:31.404
♪ How can anyone relate to me

07:31.465 --> 07:33.035
when they cannot see what I... ♪

07:33.100 --> 07:33.942
[HISSES]

07:34.001 --> 07:38.381
♪ My vampire eyes see only
blood-red skies ♪

07:38.438 --> 07:42.386
♪ Blood-red skies make tears
inside that I always hide ♪

07:42.442 --> 07:44.388
♪ So ♪

07:44.444 --> 07:47.391
♪ I walk alone ♪

07:47.447 --> 07:49.290
Pin?

07:49.349 --> 07:51.295
♪ my ♪

07:51.351 --> 07:53.126
♪ mental home ♪
- Wha-- What's it doing?

07:53.186 --> 07:55.427
♪ I can't let on ♪

07:55.489 --> 07:56.934
[BOTH GASP]

07:56.990 --> 07:58.025
[CRASH]

07:58.091 --> 07:59.468
Shh! Shh-shh-shh-shh!

07:59.526 --> 08:02.632
Oh, What?!
What happened?!

08:02.696 --> 08:03.697
Ugh!

08:05.399 --> 08:07.879
[HISSES]

08:10.370 --> 08:12.213
Where are you?!

08:12.272 --> 08:14.377
Oh, there you are.

08:14.441 --> 08:16.443
My broom.

08:18.979 --> 08:20.981
[SIGHS]

08:23.684 --> 08:25.595
Ugh. Stupid thing.

08:25.652 --> 08:26.824
Get...

08:26.887 --> 08:28.457
No! Stupid!

08:28.522 --> 08:29.523
Argh!

08:29.589 --> 08:30.590
Ugggh!

08:32.292 --> 08:33.293
Euggggh!

08:35.395 --> 08:37.102
[FAUCET SQUEAKS,
WATER SPLASHES]

08:37.164 --> 08:38.972
- Is it safe?
- I don't know, man.

08:39.032 --> 08:41.979
Go scope the scene.

08:42.034 --> 08:44.037
[MID-TEMPO MUSIC PLAYS]

08:49.643 --> 08:51.645
[MUSIC DISTORTS]

08:56.249 --> 08:57.853
What happened, man?

08:57.918 --> 08:59.226
I'm not going back out there.

08:59.286 --> 09:00.993
Well...
what do you mean?

09:01.054 --> 09:02.829
What happened?

09:02.889 --> 09:03.890
Bro?

09:06.026 --> 09:07.630
[HAIR DRYER WHIRRING]

09:15.402 --> 09:17.507
[WHIRRING STOPS]

09:17.571 --> 09:18.572
[YAWNS]

09:19.873 --> 09:21.875
[SWITCH CLICKS]

09:21.942 --> 09:22.943
[SNORING]

09:24.378 --> 09:26.119
Hmmmmm...

09:26.179 --> 09:28.181
[SNORING CONTINUES]

09:29.483 --> 09:31.485
MARCELINE:
Hmm.

09:35.722 --> 09:37.759
[CHOMPS]

09:45.065 --> 09:47.978
- Is she awake?
- Why are you talking?!

09:48.035 --> 09:49.981
I'm wondering if she's awake.

09:50.036 --> 09:52.915
Well, if she's awake, she can
definitely hear you talking!

09:52.973 --> 09:54.748
I'm whispering!

09:54.808 --> 09:57.049
Well, now we're both
quietly screaming!

09:57.110 --> 09:59.056
MARCELINE:
I can hear both of you.

09:59.112 --> 10:01.092
Disguise yourself, fool!

10:01.148 --> 10:03.424
[SWITCH CLICKS]

10:03.483 --> 10:05.656
What are you bozos doing
in my lair?

10:05.719 --> 10:07.721
Dude, I think
she sees us.

10:07.788 --> 10:09.461
What the...
Dude!

10:09.523 --> 10:11.969
You shape-changed
to look like me?!

10:12.025 --> 10:14.471
- Yeah.
- MARCELINE: Hey!

10:14.528 --> 10:17.372
Exsssplain yourselves.

10:17.431 --> 10:18.808
[EXHALES DEEPLY]

10:18.865 --> 10:20.811
We were playing hide-and-seek
in your closet,

10:20.867 --> 10:22.073
and you came home,

10:22.135 --> 10:23.614
so we hid in there all day.

10:23.670 --> 10:26.173
We saw... everything.

10:26.239 --> 10:27.377
And, oh, glob!

10:27.441 --> 10:28.920
I mean, whatever you do to us,

10:28.975 --> 10:30.682
I just want to say we're sorry!

10:30.744 --> 10:32.155
So sorry!

10:32.212 --> 10:34.249
Okay. Apology accepted.

10:34.314 --> 10:35.384
What?!

10:35.449 --> 10:38.726
I hide in your house
all the time.

10:38.785 --> 10:41.493
Anyways, no hard feelings, guys.

10:41.555 --> 10:43.557
See you soon.

10:49.529 --> 10:50.405
[SNIFFS]

10:50.464 --> 10:54.310
[HOOTING IN DISTANCE]

10:54.367 --> 10:56.369
Marceline?

10:58.672 --> 10:59.514
Jake?!

10:59.573 --> 11:00.483
[SHOWER WATER RUNNING]

11:00.540 --> 11:02.110
Jake!

11:02.175 --> 11:04.177
Hm'?

11:08.115 --> 11:09.059
Hey, man, did --

11:09.115 --> 11:10.856
[BOTH SCREAM]

11:10.917 --> 11:12.919
[HOOTS]

11:14.454 --> 11:18.425
♪ Come along with me ♪

11:18.492 --> 11:22.406
♪ and the butterflies and bees ♪

11:22.462 --> 11:26.410
♪ We can wander through the forest ♪

11:26.466 --> 11:30.414
♪ and do so as we please ♪

11:30.470 --> 11:34.441
♪ Come along with me ♪

11:34.508 --> 11:37.045
♪ to a cliff under a tree ♪

